			  			Part I: Standard page hacking<br />
<br />
-Open defense plan in a new window<br />
-Select your fleets and submit<br />
-Save the formation page as html<br />
-Open the html file in notepad<br />
-Make changes:<br />
<br />
&lt;SCRIPT TYPE=&quot;text/javascript&quot; LANGUAGE=javascript SRC=/jsLib.js&gt;&lt;/SCRIPT&gt;<br />
&lt;SCRIPT TYPE=&quot;text/javascript&quot; LANGUAGE=javascript SRC=/defense.js&gt;&lt;/SCRIPT&gt;<br />
&lt;LINK REL=&quot;stylesheet&quot; HREF=&quot;/archspace.css&quot;&gt;<br />
&lt;LINK REL=&quot;stylesheet&quot; HREF=&quot;/cssLib.css&quot;&gt;<br />
<br />
to<br />
<br />
&lt;SCRIPT TYPE=&quot;text/javascript&quot; LANGUAGE=javascript SRC=http://as.mlsecurity.com/jsLib.js&gt;&lt;/SCRIPT&gt;<br />
&lt;SCRIPT TYPE=&quot;text/javascript&quot; LANGUAGE=javascript SRC=http://as.mlsecurity.com/defense.js&gt;&lt;/SCRIPT&gt;<br />
&lt;LINK REL=&quot;stylesheet&quot; HREF=&quot;http://as.mlsecurity.com/archspace.css&quot;&gt;<br />
&lt;LINK REL=&quot;stylesheet&quot; HREF=&quot;http://as.mlsecurity.com/cssLib.css&quot;&gt;<br />
<br />
<br />
&lt;FORM METHOD=post ACTION=defense_plan_generic_result.as NAME=Fdescription&gt;<br />
<br />
to<br />
<br />
&lt;FORM METHOD=post ACTION=http://as.mlsecurity.com/archspace/war/defense_plan_generic_result.as NAME=Fdescription&gt;<br />
<br />
<br />
Part II: Bug fixing<br />
<br />
&lt;PARAM NAME=capFleet_ID VALUE=7&gt;<br />
&lt;PARAM NAME=Fleet1_ID VALUE=1&gt;<br />
&lt;PARAM NAME=Fleet2_ID VALUE=2&gt;<br />
&lt;PARAM NAME=Fleet3_ID VALUE=8&gt;<br />
<br />
to<br />
<br />
&lt;INPUT TYPE=hidden NAME=capFleet_id VALUE=7&gt;<br />
&lt;INPUT TYPE=hidden NAME=fleet2_id VALUE=1&gt;<br />
&lt;INPUT TYPE=hidden NAME=fleet3_id VALUE=2&gt;<br />
&lt;INPUT TYPE=hidden NAME=fleet4_id VALUE=8&gt;<br />
<br />
Save the file and open it in your browser.  Arrange your fleets and submit.<br />
